{
  "stem": "512.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They put on the lights that in order-- if you went five, six, feet from the wires, you were electrocuted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] One day I decided [CRYING] I had-- I didn't want to live anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I'll go to the wires and make an end.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My shadow was right behind me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She [INAUDIBLE] me, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] why are you going so close?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why-- don't you know what's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So I had to, had to go on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to abandon that idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But the selections, they would come and pull out anybody that, you know, they would-- the Nazis, the women, they were horrible, absolutely horrible.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would just walk through you and look at your face.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if they didn't like the way you looked out, they knew where you were going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were selecting always for work and for, and for the ovens.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were never selected, not my sister, not myself, because we were not, you know, we were, we were under-developed really and very frail looking.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- but life in Auschwitz was one horror, one horror, horrible nightmare.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] The selections, there one day-- there was a camp that the Czech families-- this was-- the Czech families were mostly-- they were taken early.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were taken in '41, '42, and they were together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First, they were in Theresienstadt, and then they were sent to Auschwitz, but [INAUDIBLE] whole families.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on the next to-- on the other-- like on the other block was the Czech camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They called it the Czech camp because the families were together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
